&lt;p&gt;This is an incredibly rare opportunity to join at the ground floor of a product that is already being used by millions. You will influence and execute a design vision across web and mobile, that helps consumers access unforgettable experiences at some of the finest hotels in the world. This isn&#39;t a role for someone who waits to be told what to do. We&#39;re looking for a self-starter who thrives in ambiguity, moves fast, and cares deeply about craft and impact.&lt;/p&gt;
